---
title: Sweet and Spicy Beef Stir-Fry with Ginger and Snow Peas
description: Ah, ginger and beef – the two go together like Ginger Rogers and Fred Astaire. This lip-smacking pair will be swinging across your tastebuds tonight on a bed of pillowy jasmine rice and topped with a tasty hoisin-soy sauce. This dinner is sure to have you dancing!

